sively can make you like a turtle; one who only has time to react to what has already passed.  I think a hybrid type of beast is more of what I want to be, keeping the advantage of the shell but attaining the aggressiveness of a lion as well.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulithahntalon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lith Ahntalon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 297<br> <font color=#E9D756>(5/21/02 10:26:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=300.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Share something inspirational! Why not?</span><hr size=1> Very Zen, Lurikeen.  <p><img src=http://eshamlin.home.mindspring.com/lith.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubrutas222.showPublicProfile?language=EN>brutas222</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 274<br> <font color=#E9D756>(5/21/02 10:50:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=300.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Share something inspirational! Why not?</span><hr size=1> Quote:<br>Very Zen, Lurikeen. <br><br>Bah!!  Why does everything have to have a religious connotation to it.  IMO, you are saying that his experience was based on someone else's idea.  As if his realization owes itself to something else, when in fact, his motivation was based on love and love is free. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard